title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1989-10-01
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Ramble On Rose, Walkin' Blues, Built To Last, When I Paint My Masterpiece, A Little Light, Cassidy, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Hell In A Bucket, Scarlet Begonias-> Women Are Smarter, He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door
